Exclusive to Atomic RG this 7cd mix will blow the Jackson Polloks of many an Ibiza regular. Never heard of Maurizio Benedetta rocked the motherfucking house with his madcap Italian antics and blend of Electro.
Hed Kandi flew through three hours of beautiful mixing and fab typical stylee music.
Agnelli & Nelson finished the evening with three hours of outstanding Trance building everything up nicely.
Listen out at the very end of Benedettas set where he grabs the mike fan-fecking-white-isle-tastic!
Yoshi, Mikael & James Scott up to there usual Base Bar standards. The best rated bar on the Island, you know why!!!.
